WEBVTT

01:39.500 --> 01:43.580
[Road to Success]

01:44.720 --> 01:47.900
[Episode 14]

01:50.229 --> 01:51.490
It might hurt a little.

02:03.280 --> 02:04.550
Because his heart

02:05.350 --> 02:06.590
is already here.

02:09.190 --> 02:10.000
What?

02:13.150 --> 02:14.240
I mean Wen Chengye.

02:16.910 --> 02:18.640
He may still be a bit resistant,

02:19.000 --> 02:20.060
but he came anyway.

02:22.190 --> 02:24.120
Because his heart is already here.

02:32.960 --> 02:33.710
Done.

02:34.150 --> 02:34.870
Thank you.

02:35.680 --> 02:38.140
It's going to rain.
Let's put the books away.

02:45.870 --> 02:47.590
It's starting to drizzle.

02:48.710 --> 02:50.570
You look like
you're actually enjoying this.

02:50.570 --> 02:51.480
Yeah.

02:51.510 --> 02:52.630
Hongjing is by the sea,

02:52.630 --> 02:54.040
and I grew up here.

02:54.090 --> 02:57.220
Getting caught in the rain
is just part of everyday life.

03:02.240 --> 03:03.840
The rain suddenly started pouring.
Maybe we should...

03:03.840 --> 03:05.280
Too late. Run!

03:16.360 --> 03:18.430
♪ I caught your eyes ♪

03:18.900 --> 03:21.270
♪ On the summer night ♪

03:21.760 --> 03:27.270
♪ Like stars that glow so bright ♪

03:23.680 --> 03:24.530
I

03:25.360 --> 03:27.290
don't hate rainy days anymore.

03:28.790 --> 03:31.050
♪ A spark in my heart ♪

03:31.750 --> 03:37.540
♪ Lost in a dream secretly ♪

03:31.840 --> 03:33.120
Because...

03:40.930 --> 03:46.350
♪ With the evening breeze
whispering in my ear ♪

03:47.079 --> 03:52.880
♪ Fireworks bloom across the sky ♪

03:53.310 --> 03:56.000
♪ Shimmering in your eyes ♪

03:54.960 --> 03:56.020
Come on, slow down.

03:56.260 --> 04:02.630
♪ And spreading into
a gentle sea of stars ♪

03:56.920 --> 03:58.579
Watch the stairs. Be careful.

04:11.470 --> 04:12.870
What are you laughing at?

04:13.280 --> 04:14.240
I'm laughing at you.

04:14.240 --> 04:17.300
You've probably never
looked this disheveled before.

04:19.040 --> 04:19.700
Hold still.

04:30.720 --> 04:32.600
Your eyes are so important.

04:32.600 --> 04:34.460
We can't let anything get in them.

04:37.430 --> 04:39.430
I thought it was something serious.

05:16.800 --> 05:19.060
You've got raindrops on your eyelashes.

05:23.560 --> 05:25.960
Your eyes are also
very important, Ms. Lin.

05:31.120 --> 05:32.560
Hurry and take a hot shower.

05:32.560 --> 05:33.670
Don't catch a cold.

05:54.370 --> 05:57.720
[Director Qian]

05:54.850 --> 05:55.800
Lin,

05:56.310 --> 05:58.630
you can get a temporary pass

05:58.630 --> 05:59.610
for Coach Wang.

05:59.830 --> 06:02.690
Just create an account for him
in the school system.

06:03.560 --> 06:04.750
Also, keep the monthly exam

06:04.750 --> 06:06.000
in mind.

06:06.000 --> 06:07.930
Understood. Thank you, Director.

06:21.080 --> 06:23.060
[Hongjing No. 8 High School]

06:24.850 --> 06:26.130
[This account is already registered.
Please enter a different one.]

06:27.280 --> 06:28.750
I need another number...

06:32.560 --> 06:33.450
Oh, right.

06:33.520 --> 06:35.060
I have another QQ account.

06:38.540 --> 06:40.020
[This account is already registered.
Please enter a different one.]

06:41.940 --> 06:42.900
[Phone Number/Email/QQ]

06:44.980 --> 06:47.290
[Username: Wang Fa]

06:47.360 --> 06:48.980
[Password] [Your password is too short.
Please choose a new password.]

06:49.050 --> 06:49.880
[Your password is weak.]

06:49.909 --> 06:51.170
[Your password is not strong enough.]

06:52.500 --> 06:53.760
[Hello, Mr. Wang Fa.]

06:56.240 --> 06:57.290
Coach Wang,

06:57.430 --> 07:00.320
I hope
this unrestricted campus access pass

07:00.340 --> 07:02.590
gives you a sense of belonging.

07:15.490 --> 07:19.340
[Slack Superstar]

07:16.120 --> 07:17.980
I got your access pass sorted out.

07:20.410 --> 07:22.790
♪ Night slips through my fingers ♪

07:23.640 --> 07:27.480
♪ Embracing the coldness of wakefulness ♪

07:28.370 --> 07:30.180
♪ Whispering my thoughts alone ♪

07:30.710 --> 07:35.610
♪ Saying goodbye to the evening breeze
we met by chance ♪

07:36.200 --> 07:38.850
♪ Staying with the jasmine blossoms
until late spring ♪

07:39.520 --> 07:42.610
♪ Watching their elegance fade,
their fragrance disappear ♪

07:43.909 --> 07:46.930
♪ I once dreamed of beauty ♪

07:45.720 --> 07:47.650
The rain in Hongjing is beautiful.

07:47.850 --> 07:51.710
♪ And I accept that
regrets may grow wild ♪

07:51.820 --> 07:53.140
[The rain in Hongjing is beautiful.]

07:52.390 --> 07:54.590
♪ Look, beneath the sunlight ♪

07:55.390 --> 07:59.310
♪ In the dancing specks of dust ♪

08:00.100 --> 08:02.860
♪ I'm grateful I never lost my sincerity ♪

08:01.480 --> 08:04.670
[Slack Superstar]

08:02.570 --> 08:04.620
How about I teach you
how to ride a bike sometime?

08:03.520 --> 08:07.290
♪ Or my gift for happiness ♪

08:07.390 --> 08:08.590
What beautiful rain?

08:08.860 --> 08:09.650
♪ In the rain ♪

08:09.190 --> 08:10.600
Messaging Ms. Lin, huh?

08:13.310 --> 08:15.910
I never should've given you
the key to my place.

08:24.390 --> 08:25.650
You've fallen for her.

08:28.750 --> 08:30.270
You actually hesitated.

08:33.720 --> 08:35.270
Don't you have anything better to do?

08:35.270 --> 08:37.150
Is Hengjiu Club really paying you
to sit around like this?

08:37.150 --> 08:39.870
Now that's a classic change of subject.

08:42.080 --> 08:42.929
Tell you what.

08:43.039 --> 08:44.500
Let me help you out.

08:44.840 --> 08:46.300
I'll help you win her over.

08:46.440 --> 08:47.120
You?

08:50.310 --> 08:52.610
[Slack Superstar]

08:58.890 --> 09:00.120
Up for a drink?

09:00.960 --> 09:02.750
Bring out the good stuff, and I'm in.

09:02.750 --> 09:03.680
Very good stuff.

09:05.440 --> 09:07.270
That's more like it.

09:11.390 --> 09:13.150
Overall, this book

09:13.150 --> 09:14.750
covers famous

09:14.750 --> 09:16.070
historical figures,

09:16.070 --> 09:18.450
key moments in history,
and historical facts.

09:18.450 --> 09:21.310
It's essentially
a narrative-style history book.

09:21.440 --> 09:22.200
Very good.

09:22.510 --> 09:23.570
Thank you, Ms. Lin.

09:23.630 --> 09:24.690
Let's begin class.

09:25.270 --> 09:26.150
-So?
-How'd it go?

09:26.150 --> 09:26.560
Did you pass?

09:26.560 --> 09:28.020
-Did you pass?
-Nailed it.

09:30.720 --> 09:31.240
Here she comes.

09:31.240 --> 09:33.270
You've all finished today's reading

09:33.270 --> 09:34.550
and oral retelling assignment.

09:34.550 --> 09:36.030
The purpose of this exercise

09:36.030 --> 09:37.750
is to improve your concentration.

09:37.750 --> 09:39.840
Learning is a game of efficiency.

09:39.840 --> 09:42.970
Congratulations, everyone,
on completing Lesson One.

09:45.960 --> 09:47.690
Next, I'd like to ask you a question.

09:47.690 --> 09:50.020
Why do you want to improve?

09:51.320 --> 09:52.630
Because if we don't do well
on the next monthly exam,

09:52.630 --> 09:54.240
we won't be allowed to play football.

09:54.240 --> 09:55.550
-Right. We want to keep playing football.
-Play football.

09:55.550 --> 09:56.630
-Right. We want to play football.
-Play football.

09:56.630 --> 09:57.390
Very good.

10:02.550 --> 10:04.120
Interest.

10:04.750 --> 10:06.630
-Interest.
-Interest.

10:07.910 --> 10:10.000
-Drive.
-Drive.

10:11.080 --> 10:13.270
-Feedback.
-Feedback.

10:13.270 --> 10:14.030
What does that mean?

10:14.030 --> 10:15.600
-No idea.
-I don't know.

10:17.390 --> 10:18.910
Feedback.

10:21.790 --> 10:23.390
Next, let's move on to

10:23.390 --> 10:25.390
the second lesson of Yuanyuan's Classroom.

10:25.390 --> 10:27.670
Interest is the greatest driving force.

10:27.670 --> 10:29.000
Let me ask you something.

10:29.000 --> 10:30.270
When you're introduced

10:30.270 --> 10:32.080
to something unfamiliar,

10:32.080 --> 10:33.680
what's your first reaction?

10:35.440 --> 10:36.440
Fear, I guess.

10:37.550 --> 10:38.440
Exactly,

10:38.440 --> 10:39.670
scared.

10:39.670 --> 10:42.150
So today, I want you to
learn to start from

10:42.150 --> 10:43.630
what you're familiar with

10:43.630 --> 10:45.320
and what interests you,

10:45.320 --> 10:47.790
and use scientific learning methods
to make progress.

10:47.790 --> 10:49.910
Ms. Lin, how do we start

10:49.910 --> 10:52.970
from something
we're familiar with and interested in?

10:53.200 --> 10:54.360
Do you know

10:54.360 --> 10:56.550
what people usually learn first
when studying

10:56.550 --> 10:58.350
a foreign language or a dialect?

10:58.790 --> 11:00.510
Swear words, of course.

11:01.840 --> 11:04.870
-Let's do Classical Chinese insults.
-Insults?

11:04.870 --> 11:06.390
Can anyone think of some
that everybody knows?

11:06.390 --> 11:07.390
Go ahead.

11:07.390 --> 11:08.190
Chen Jianghe.

11:10.270 --> 11:12.750
"R-Rotten wood cannot be carved;

11:13.480 --> 11:15.750
a wall of dung cannot be plastered."

11:17.080 --> 11:17.840
Qin Ao.

11:21.630 --> 11:23.160
I'll allow you to look it up.

11:23.840 --> 11:26.200
Looks like what I just said
fits you perfectly.

11:26.200 --> 11:27.130
You rotten wood.

11:30.960 --> 11:32.490
I'll look something up too.

11:33.790 --> 11:37.390
"This brat is not worthy of
conspiring over important matters."

11:38.550 --> 11:39.360
Explain it.

11:40.790 --> 11:41.790
It means,

11:41.790 --> 11:45.590
"A stupid boy like you doesn't deserve to
discuss strategy with me."

11:45.630 --> 11:48.490
"People say Chu men
are just monkeys wearing hats."

11:48.600 --> 11:51.600
You're indeed all show—

11:51.910 --> 11:54.870
literally a monkey in a hat.

11:55.390 --> 11:56.030
Poser.

11:58.080 --> 11:58.910
Just you wait.

12:00.320 --> 12:01.390
"Shameless and scheming,

12:01.390 --> 12:03.120
returning like driven flies."

12:03.200 --> 12:04.910
You're a petty opportunist,
buzzing around like a fly,

12:04.910 --> 12:07.270
clinging to life like a mangy dog!

12:07.870 --> 12:09.200
"You, gaunt as a turtledove,
sallow as a starving crane,

12:09.200 --> 12:11.130
how dare you speak such nonsense?"

12:13.790 --> 12:15.390
Make one up. Insult him back.

12:16.390 --> 12:18.030
He just called you skinny as a turtledove,

12:18.030 --> 12:19.200
with a face as pale as a starving crane—

12:19.200 --> 12:20.320
weak and ugly.

12:21.910 --> 12:22.910
Just you wait.

12:22.910 --> 12:24.390
Come on. Come on.

12:24.390 --> 12:25.120
Too weak.

12:27.200 --> 12:28.510
Got it.

12:28.510 --> 12:30.480
With the head of a muntjac
and the eyes of a rat,

12:30.480 --> 12:32.010
you can only be up to no good!

12:33.670 --> 12:35.270
I can insult people
in Classical Chinese now!

12:35.270 --> 12:36.360
That's progress.

12:36.870 --> 12:38.200
You brat!

12:38.200 --> 12:39.660
Impressive, impressive.

12:41.080 --> 12:42.270
You, a pile of dry bones in a grave—

12:42.270 --> 12:43.930
hardly worth worrying about.

12:44.150 --> 12:45.320
He really learned it.

12:45.320 --> 12:46.270
He really did.

12:46.270 --> 12:47.270
Impressive.

12:47.270 --> 12:48.670
Qin Ao, you memorized it

12:48.670 --> 12:49.790
word for word.

12:50.790 --> 12:52.030
You've grown up.

12:52.030 --> 12:53.200
Amazing, amazing.

12:53.200 --> 12:54.440
Let's give Qin Ao a round of applause.

12:54.440 --> 12:55.670
Very good.

13:07.730 --> 13:13.520
[Math, Physics, Chemistry] [Chinese]

13:08.200 --> 13:09.790
You should all know

13:09.790 --> 13:11.000
it's clearly impossible to

13:11.000 --> 13:12.510
raise your grades in every subject

13:12.510 --> 13:14.170
in such a short period of time.

13:15.380 --> 13:18.590
[Math, Physics, Chemistry] [Chinese]

13:16.790 --> 13:19.320
The first three multi-step questions
in math,

13:19.320 --> 13:21.480
physics, and chemistry cover concepts
that are relatively simple.

13:21.480 --> 13:22.670
We can master them

13:22.670 --> 13:24.670
through practice problems
and memorizing formulas.

13:24.670 --> 13:26.270
They are basically free points.

13:26.270 --> 13:27.530
There's another area.

13:27.560 --> 13:29.790
[Math, Physics, Chemistry] [Chinese]

13:28.030 --> 13:30.320
The Classical Chinese section
on the Chinese exam

13:30.320 --> 13:31.740
is also one of the easiest places to gain

13:31.740 --> 13:33.300
the most points with the least effort.

13:33.300 --> 13:40.430
[Math, Physics, Chemistry] [Chinese]

13:34.440 --> 13:36.320
By breaking through these two sections—

13:36.320 --> 13:37.790
using interest as your driving force,

13:37.790 --> 13:39.030
like I just taught you—

13:39.030 --> 13:41.030
you can tap into your own potential.

13:44.150 --> 13:45.350
Look straight ahead.

13:45.790 --> 13:47.320
You have to hold on to my bike, okay?

13:47.320 --> 13:48.230
Relax.

13:49.240 --> 13:50.970
Keep the handlebars straight.

13:54.790 --> 13:55.550
Turn right.

13:57.080 --> 13:58.200
To the right.

13:58.200 --> 13:59.550
Your right hand.

13:59.550 --> 14:01.610
That's it. Rest it on the brake lever.

14:01.910 --> 14:03.240
Not that hand. Right hand. Right.

14:03.240 --> 14:04.900
This is left. Your right hand.

14:06.510 --> 14:07.360
Pick up a little speed.

14:07.360 --> 14:08.960
Straighten the handlebars.

14:09.480 --> 14:11.270
Promise you won't let go!

14:11.270 --> 14:13.480
Don't let me fall!

14:13.480 --> 14:15.240
Relax. I've got you.

14:18.510 --> 14:20.200
There's a bridge ahead.
I can't make it up.

14:20.200 --> 14:21.630
Then try turning.

14:21.630 --> 14:22.480
To the left.

14:28.910 --> 14:30.120
I'm tipping over. I'm falling!

14:30.120 --> 14:30.910
I've got you.

14:30.990 --> 14:32.090
I turned.

14:32.720 --> 14:33.630
Keep your eyes forward.

14:33.630 --> 14:36.160
-Speed up.
-I think I'm getting the hang of it.

14:38.720 --> 14:40.270
Good job, Ms. Lin.

14:43.030 --> 14:44.150
You absolutely cannot let go.

14:44.150 --> 14:45.440
Don't worry. I won't.

14:45.670 --> 14:46.790
I learned it.

14:49.270 --> 14:50.630
I learned it!

14:58.130 --> 14:59.400
♪ Time's passing by ♪

15:00.060 --> 15:01.790
♪ Nothing remains ♪

15:00.320 --> 15:01.000
Wang Fa.

15:01.000 --> 15:02.110
Wang Fa!

15:02.440 --> 15:03.720
You let go!

15:03.040 --> 15:05.720
♪ All the dreamers awake alone ♪

15:04.240 --> 15:05.440
I learned it.

15:05.720 --> 15:06.790
Congratulations.

15:06.310 --> 15:07.960
♪ Shadows above ♪

15:07.000 --> 15:09.120
From now on, it'll be my turn
to give you rides.

15:08.800 --> 15:10.580
♪ Rain falls around ♪

15:09.120 --> 15:10.910
Ms. Lin's got big ambitions.

15:10.910 --> 15:12.150
Then I'll look forward to it.

15:11.090 --> 15:11.790
♪ In your arms ♪

15:12.700 --> 15:14.150
♪ We become one ♪

15:14.640 --> 15:16.180
♪ Through day and night ♪

15:17.040 --> 15:19.410
♪ I can see you ♪

15:20.380 --> 15:22.620
♪ In my eyes ♪

15:23.340 --> 15:24.790
♪ Just hold me tight ♪

15:25.630 --> 15:30.970
♪ Look into my soul so deeply ♪

15:32.210 --> 15:33.610
♪ Rainbow sunlight ♪

15:34.350 --> 15:35.490
♪ Painful tears are gone ♪

15:36.660 --> 15:37.400
♪ Wonderful dreams ♪

15:38.410 --> 15:39.760
♪ Are so close to me ♪

15:41.080 --> 15:41.970
♪ Memories fly ♪

15:42.860 --> 15:44.110
♪ Leave them all behind ♪

15:45.130 --> 15:50.730
♪ Just take my hand and stay with me ♪

16:09.650 --> 16:11.820
♪ Two souls aligned ♪

16:13.520 --> 16:15.440
♪ In silent gravity ♪

16:15.330 --> 16:16.790
[Studied in the UK; psychology major]

16:16.820 --> 16:18.910
[Loves spicy food; hates coriander]

16:17.670 --> 16:19.800
♪ Heal my heart ♪

16:20.420 --> 16:22.930
♪ With every part of you ♪

16:21.870 --> 16:24.120
Have you ever heard of drinking wontons?

16:24.120 --> 16:26.320
For wontons like these, with thin wrappers
and just a little filling,

16:25.610 --> 16:27.500
♪ Our words flow ♪

16:26.320 --> 16:28.380
you can just drink them with the soup.

16:29.080 --> 16:31.080
♪ A gentle stream ♪

16:31.610 --> 16:33.340
[Bad at sports; can't ride a bike]

16:33.390 --> 16:35.570
♪ They glow like fireflies ♪

16:35.080 --> 16:36.540
This is called cheating.

16:36.220 --> 16:38.740
♪ Inside a silken dream ♪

16:36.790 --> 16:37.910
What do you know?

16:37.910 --> 16:40.170
This is called strategic intelligence.

16:40.950 --> 16:42.650
[Fireflies expert]

16:40.950 --> 16:46.860
♪ We talk the cool night, breeze away ♪

16:43.030 --> 16:45.330
But when they gather together,

16:45.440 --> 16:47.900
they light the way
for those moving forward.

16:48.270 --> 16:50.440
And with their tiny glimmers,

16:48.780 --> 16:50.400
♪ We trace the roads ♪

16:50.440 --> 16:52.120
they show that every life has value.

16:51.180 --> 16:54.290
♪ That never see an end ♪

16:52.150 --> 16:53.340
[Advocates natural selection]

16:53.360 --> 16:56.930
[Computer ID: Spade Q]
[Highly competitive]

16:56.970 --> 17:00.380
♪ We softly calm the hidden doubt ♪

17:01.170 --> 17:05.780
♪ Seen in each other's eyes ♪

17:06.440 --> 17:10.410
♪ And wake the warmth inside ♪

17:10.310 --> 17:12.880
Go, Hongjing No. 8 High School!

17:12.170 --> 17:14.589
♪ Life begins alone ♪

17:15.319 --> 17:18.230
♪ A road we walk alone ♪

17:16.109 --> 17:19.260
[Spade Q—Lin Wanxing] [Probability: 0%]

17:19.329 --> 17:20.530
[Advocates natural selection]

17:19.920 --> 17:22.329
♪ Until fate brings warmth ♪

17:20.640 --> 17:22.940
Now there are so many people and things...

17:22.940 --> 17:26.380
♪ To light our way back home ♪

17:24.880 --> 17:26.680
I can't bear to let go of.

17:28.490 --> 17:30.190
♪ True love is not just ♪

17:30.950 --> 17:32.550
♪ The gaze when two hearts first meet ♪

17:32.400 --> 17:34.000
Even though

17:33.460 --> 17:38.360
♪ It's courage in the arms ♪

17:34.000 --> 17:35.600
I don't really want you to go,

17:36.240 --> 17:38.160
I've decided that whether you stay

17:38.160 --> 17:39.420
or leave,

17:39.680 --> 17:42.310
I'll lead them
and help them keep playing their best.

17:40.270 --> 17:42.540
♪ We stand as one ♪

17:44.040 --> 17:45.940
♪ Our words flow ♪

17:45.810 --> 17:49.870
[Spade Q—Lin Wanxing] [Probability: 0%]

17:47.660 --> 17:49.720
♪ A gentle stream ♪

17:51.810 --> 17:53.990
♪ They glow like fireflies ♪

17:54.640 --> 17:56.280
♪ Inside a silken dream ♪

18:08.480 --> 18:09.510
What does this classical text mean?

18:09.510 --> 18:11.110
The annotation only says this:

18:11.110 --> 18:12.200
"Zhang" means "grow."

18:12.200 --> 18:13.640
Do you know what it means?

18:14.480 --> 18:15.200
I don't know either.

18:15.200 --> 18:16.800
Just look it up on your phone.

18:18.440 --> 18:19.830
My brain works better than a phone.

18:19.830 --> 18:21.230
Which sentence? Read it.

18:22.070 --> 18:23.240
The first one.

18:23.240 --> 18:26.480
"Your servant has heard that
whoever seeks a tree's vigorous growth..."

18:24.590 --> 18:26.530
[Ten Recommendations
to Emperor Taizong of Tang]

18:26.480 --> 18:27.350
Is this zhang ("to grow")
or chang ("long")?

18:27.350 --> 18:28.410
What are you doing?

18:29.310 --> 18:30.440
Go back to your seat.

18:35.240 --> 18:36.300
What are you doing?

18:37.000 --> 18:39.240
There was a line in the Classical Chinese text
that we didn't understand,

18:39.240 --> 18:40.510
so we looked up the annotation.

18:40.510 --> 18:42.070
I don't care what you were doing.

18:42.070 --> 18:44.640
Don't you know
phones are strictly prohibited at school?

18:44.640 --> 18:46.000
No, we really didn't know it.

18:46.000 --> 18:48.590
-We really only looked up the annotation.
-Hand over your phone.

18:48.590 --> 18:49.420
Hurry up.

18:49.530 --> 18:51.390
-We really weren't...
-Hurry up!

18:52.580 --> 18:57.500
[Fight for your youth!]

18:54.350 --> 18:55.070
What are you looking at?

18:55.070 --> 18:56.270
Get back to studying.

18:58.350 --> 18:59.200
You two,

18:59.610 --> 19:01.110
go out and reflect on your actions.

19:01.110 --> 19:01.750
Go!

19:04.160 --> 19:04.920
Now!

19:07.070 --> 19:07.980
Hurry.

19:08.720 --> 19:10.200
We only looked up the annotation...

19:09.430 --> 19:12.870
[Fight for your youth!]

19:10.200 --> 19:11.600
What are you laughing at?

19:15.000 --> 19:15.920
Study hard.

19:20.440 --> 19:21.100
Boss,

19:21.510 --> 19:22.550
even if we're reflecting,

19:22.550 --> 19:23.440
do we really have to run laps?

19:23.440 --> 19:24.350
Just think of it as training.

19:24.350 --> 19:26.720
Why do you think
Mr. Jin wouldn't believe us?

19:26.720 --> 19:27.980
You're really stupid.

19:28.110 --> 19:30.370
You actually expected him to believe us?

19:31.880 --> 19:32.540
Wait, Boss.

19:32.960 --> 19:33.510
What?

19:35.830 --> 19:38.630
I ate something bad for lunch,
and my stomach...

19:39.090 --> 19:40.010
Go.

19:40.590 --> 19:42.790
Why is there always something with you?

19:46.270 --> 19:47.790
It hurts so much. You...

19:48.200 --> 19:49.440
Does yours not hurt?

19:49.830 --> 19:50.590
No.

19:50.590 --> 19:51.720
Only you.

19:53.680 --> 19:55.610
I seriously can't hold it anymore.

19:57.720 --> 19:59.320
Do you have any toilet paper?

20:00.880 --> 20:01.510
I...

20:12.640 --> 20:13.900
You've got some nerve.

20:14.550 --> 20:15.640
I told you to bring it, but you didn't.

20:15.640 --> 20:17.440
Then you had the guts
to snitch to the teacher?

20:17.440 --> 20:18.350
I didn't.

20:19.160 --> 20:20.750
-Stand still.
-Boss.

20:21.350 --> 20:22.400
Boss.

20:22.400 --> 20:25.110
-What?
-Something's going on here.

20:25.640 --> 20:26.350
Why are you dodging?

20:26.350 --> 20:27.160
Lift your head.

20:27.160 --> 20:28.350
-What's going on?
-Listen to this.

20:28.350 --> 20:30.680
Do I have to beat you
before you'll look up?

20:31.550 --> 20:32.640
Do you believe

20:32.640 --> 20:34.180
that I'll make your life miserable
at this school?

20:34.180 --> 20:35.840
Come here. Help me up.

20:36.440 --> 20:38.340
I didn't. I really didn't.

20:38.480 --> 20:40.640
You dare sneak off and tell the teacher

20:40.640 --> 20:42.300
that we've been bullying you?

20:42.640 --> 20:43.530
Me,

20:43.690 --> 20:45.690
the top student in the entire grade.

20:46.070 --> 20:47.870
Do you think they'd believe you?

20:56.480 --> 20:57.140
Go.

20:57.170 --> 20:58.120
Pick it up.

21:00.920 --> 21:01.790
Hurry up.

21:08.750 --> 21:09.440
Say,

21:09.880 --> 21:10.790
"I'm a snitch."

21:11.750 --> 21:12.790
I'm a snitch.

21:13.240 --> 21:14.310
I'm a snitch.

21:14.310 --> 21:15.720
Louder.

21:15.720 --> 21:17.440
-I'm a snitch.
-Bastards.

21:20.310 --> 21:21.240
I'm a snitch.

21:21.550 --> 21:22.680
I'm a snitch.

21:22.920 --> 21:24.110
I'm a snitch.

21:24.110 --> 21:25.670
I'm a snitch.

21:26.240 --> 21:27.480
I'm a snitch.

21:28.030 --> 21:29.090
What are you doing?

21:30.160 --> 21:31.000
Alright.

21:31.000 --> 21:32.000
It's alright now.

21:32.270 --> 21:33.530
Let's go back to class.

21:34.440 --> 21:35.840
Did I say you could leave?

21:36.440 --> 21:37.350
Come with me to see Director Jin.

21:37.350 --> 21:39.160
I'd advise you to stay out of this.

21:39.160 --> 21:40.640
And even if we do go,

21:41.510 --> 21:43.370
who do you think they'll believe?

21:44.400 --> 21:46.400
You lot still think you can play football?

21:46.400 --> 21:47.200
What a joke.

21:47.790 --> 21:49.070
You lot are just a disgrace to the school.

21:49.070 --> 21:49.880
Who's the disgrace here?

21:49.880 --> 21:50.610
Let go!

21:50.630 --> 21:51.830
-Don't start a fight!
-What are you doing?

21:51.830 --> 21:53.880
-Back off!
-You wanna fight?

21:53.900 --> 21:54.860
-What do you want?
-What are you doing?

21:54.860 --> 21:56.860
-Get out of the way!
-Go away!

21:57.480 --> 21:58.070
Hit me?

21:58.070 --> 21:59.270
Think you can beat me?

22:00.920 --> 22:01.650
Let go of him!

22:02.640 --> 22:04.350
Boss, stop fighting!

22:04.350 --> 22:05.160
Boss!

22:05.160 --> 22:06.400
D-Don't fight, Boss!

22:06.400 --> 22:07.070
Let go!

22:08.070 --> 22:10.030
Boss, don't fight!

22:10.030 --> 22:10.920
Let him go!

22:10.920 --> 22:11.880
Boss, let him go!

22:11.880 --> 22:12.790
They're fighting.

22:12.790 --> 22:13.720
Who's fighting?

22:13.750 --> 22:14.720
What are you doing?

22:14.720 --> 22:16.030
Let's go get a teacher. Let's go.

22:16.030 --> 22:18.240
Stop fighting! That's enough!

22:19.070 --> 22:20.310
-Let go!
-That's enough, Boss!

22:20.310 --> 22:22.640
I was just memorizing vocabulary
in the garden.

22:22.640 --> 22:23.960
Then I thought
I'd eaten something bad at lunch,

22:23.960 --> 22:25.440
so I wanted to use the restroom.

22:25.440 --> 22:27.000
At the restroom entrance,

22:27.110 --> 22:29.040
I accidentally bumped into Qin Ao.

22:29.110 --> 22:30.830
Then he suddenly shoved me.

22:31.400 --> 22:33.400
I tried to block him, and he hit me.

22:33.400 --> 22:34.030
Director, look,

22:34.030 --> 22:35.270
he beat me up like this.

22:35.270 --> 22:36.400
Rao Di only got into the fight

22:36.400 --> 22:37.110
with them

22:37.110 --> 22:38.240
because he was trying to protect me.

22:38.240 --> 22:39.510
What are you talking about?

22:39.510 --> 22:40.390
Director,

22:40.550 --> 22:42.070
they were the ones who started it.

22:42.070 --> 22:43.790
I saw them bullying another student.

22:43.790 --> 22:45.590
I was the one protecting someone.

22:45.590 --> 22:47.110
So you're admitting you shoved him?

22:47.110 --> 22:48.070
No!

22:48.070 --> 22:49.480
They hit Lin Lu first,

22:49.480 --> 22:50.550
and I was only fighting back!

22:50.550 --> 22:51.590
You're lying.

22:51.590 --> 22:53.000
How could I possibly hit someone?

22:53.000 --> 22:54.550
The college entrance exam is coming up.

22:54.550 --> 22:55.900
My grades are so good.

22:55.920 --> 22:57.780
Getting into a fight
would only hurt my exam results.

22:57.780 --> 22:59.030
How could I possibly do that?

22:59.030 --> 23:00.750
Impossible for you, but possible for me—
is that it?

23:00.750 --> 23:02.440
The whole school knows
you have a bad temper.

23:02.440 --> 23:03.350
You tell me if it's possible.

23:03.350 --> 23:04.640
Impossible!

23:04.640 --> 23:06.550
Director, I'll say it one more time—

23:06.550 --> 23:07.400
I didn't start it!

23:07.400 --> 23:08.880
I just didn't!

23:08.880 --> 23:10.830
And I saw them bullying another student!

23:10.830 --> 23:12.200
Wasn't I supposed to stand up for him?

23:12.200 --> 23:13.080
Qin Ao,

23:13.160 --> 23:14.690
what are you yelling about?

23:15.030 --> 23:15.880
Instead of studying hard,

23:15.880 --> 23:17.350
you go around
fighting and causing trouble.

23:17.350 --> 23:19.750
Are you looking for a disciplinary record?

23:20.720 --> 23:23.480
Director, Wu Yunqi is really lying.

23:23.480 --> 23:25.640
The student they bullied
is from Class 4, Grade 11.

23:25.640 --> 23:27.310
Everyone calls him Little Mouse.

23:27.310 --> 23:29.720
They got all his books dirty
and stomped on them.

23:29.720 --> 23:32.580
Director, if you don't believe us,
you can go check.

23:34.440 --> 23:35.270
Mr. Wang.

23:35.830 --> 23:36.590
Director Jin.

23:36.590 --> 23:38.640
Go to Class 4 and see
if there's such a student.

23:38.640 --> 23:40.000
If so, bring him here.

23:40.590 --> 23:41.510
And his backpack.

23:41.510 --> 23:42.240
Okay.

23:46.960 --> 23:47.960
Qin Ao, Lin Lu,

23:47.960 --> 23:50.620
both of you stand properly
with your heads down.

24:02.550 --> 24:03.350
Director Jin.

24:10.200 --> 24:10.880
Hey,

24:11.440 --> 24:12.750
tell the Director the truth.

24:12.750 --> 24:14.030
How did those two jerks bully you?

24:14.030 --> 24:16.090
It's okay. Don't be afraid. I'm here.

24:17.720 --> 24:18.670
Student,

24:18.960 --> 24:20.180
what's your name?

24:20.350 --> 24:21.400
Gu Yihao.

24:21.400 --> 24:22.410
Gu Yihao,

24:22.590 --> 24:24.350
you don't need to worry about anything.

24:24.350 --> 24:25.160
Tell me,

24:25.440 --> 24:26.790
just now during the break,

24:26.790 --> 24:29.190
did anyone bully you outside the restroom?

24:33.680 --> 24:34.470
No.

24:35.750 --> 24:37.010
I didn't go downstairs

24:37.200 --> 24:38.270
during the break.

24:38.270 --> 24:39.000
No.

24:39.440 --> 24:40.030
You can

24:40.030 --> 24:41.550
tell the truth. I'm here. It's okay.

24:41.550 --> 24:43.150
Tell the Director the truth.

24:51.160 --> 24:53.110
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

24:53.920 --> 24:54.790
I wasn't lying.

24:54.790 --> 24:56.510
Impossible! Give me your bag.

24:59.350 --> 25:00.680
These are not his books.

25:04.680 --> 25:06.070
His name isn't on them.

25:07.720 --> 25:09.110
They must've switched his books, Director.

25:09.110 --> 25:10.030
Wait, where are your books?

25:10.030 --> 25:11.070
These aren't your books.

25:11.070 --> 25:13.160
Enough, both of you.

25:13.160 --> 25:14.100
Hey,

25:14.350 --> 25:15.680
what do you mean by this?

25:15.750 --> 25:16.640
They bullied you like that,

25:16.640 --> 25:17.590
and we stood up for you.

25:17.590 --> 25:18.640
Why are you doing this?

25:18.640 --> 25:19.270
Qin Ao,

25:19.270 --> 25:20.590
are you going to slander another student?

25:20.590 --> 25:21.200
No,

25:21.200 --> 25:21.790
Director.

25:21.790 --> 25:22.960
-Everything I said is...
-Mr. Wang,

25:22.960 --> 25:24.510
send the three of them back to class,

25:24.510 --> 25:25.240
alright?

25:25.240 --> 25:26.510
Pack up your things.

25:26.790 --> 25:27.920
Goodbye, Director.

25:28.030 --> 25:28.960
Go back and focus on your lessons.

25:28.960 --> 25:29.680
Okay.

25:35.680 --> 25:36.830
Jin Laoyao!

25:36.830 --> 25:38.160
What do you mean by this?

25:38.640 --> 25:40.550
Just because they get good grades

25:40.550 --> 25:41.920
and we don't,

25:41.920 --> 25:43.780
you're covering for them, right?

25:43.790 --> 25:44.680
What did you just call me?

25:44.680 --> 25:45.640
Jin Laoyao!

25:46.480 --> 25:47.480
Qin Ao,

25:48.240 --> 25:49.750
instead of studying hard,

25:49.750 --> 25:51.030
you falsely accuse other students,

25:51.030 --> 25:53.070
and now you're even
disrespecting your teacher.

25:53.070 --> 25:53.640
You...

25:54.200 --> 25:56.440
call your parents to come over.

25:56.440 --> 25:57.000
Fine!

25:57.000 --> 25:58.440
-Call them right now.
-You think I'm scared?

25:58.440 --> 25:59.200
Call them.

26:06.330 --> 26:07.340
Director Jin,

26:07.880 --> 26:09.400
I'm Qin Ao's father.

26:09.400 --> 26:10.200
You're here.

26:11.830 --> 26:13.160
These two students

26:13.160 --> 26:14.510
were playing on their phones in class,

26:14.510 --> 26:15.680
got into a fight,

26:15.680 --> 26:18.080
and even slandered other students. And...

26:18.830 --> 26:20.680
Director, our Lu

26:20.680 --> 26:23.160
isn't the type to bully other students.

26:23.160 --> 26:24.880
Why don't you look into it again?

26:24.880 --> 26:26.160
We already have.

26:26.160 --> 26:28.070
We brought in the student they mentioned

26:28.070 --> 26:29.070
and asked him clearly.

26:29.070 --> 26:31.070
The things they said didn't happen.

26:33.480 --> 26:34.390
Tell me.

26:34.550 --> 26:35.440
What happened?

26:37.240 --> 26:38.480
How many times do I have to say it?

26:38.480 --> 26:40.440
We were just on our way to the restroom

26:40.440 --> 26:41.920
when we saw another student being bullied.

26:41.920 --> 26:43.240
We stepped in to help.

26:43.240 --> 26:44.480
And they threw the first punch.

26:44.480 --> 26:45.270
Got it?

26:45.270 --> 26:47.000
We're not lying at all.

26:48.270 --> 26:49.110
Mr. Qin,

26:49.960 --> 26:51.160
I hate to say this,

26:51.160 --> 26:53.720
but his slandering of other students
is a matter of character.

26:53.720 --> 26:55.480
He has to face disciplinary action!

26:55.480 --> 26:57.000
You're the one framing me!

26:57.000 --> 26:59.180
Qin Ao, watch your attitude!

26:59.400 --> 27:02.000
He framed me,
and I'm the one getting a demerit?

27:02.000 --> 27:03.920
-Do you even deserve to be a teacher?
-You!

27:03.920 --> 27:04.880
Watch how you speak!

27:04.880 --> 27:05.830
Apologize to your teacher!

27:05.830 --> 27:07.920
I didn't do anything wrong!
Why should I apologize?

27:07.920 --> 27:08.960
Apologize now!

27:11.960 --> 27:13.830
You're getting more and more unruly.

27:13.830 --> 27:15.560
Are you planning to quit school

27:15.590 --> 27:16.920
and go haul bricks on a construction site?

27:16.920 --> 27:18.200
I'll say it one last time!

27:18.200 --> 27:19.880
I didn't lie, and I did nothing wrong!

27:19.880 --> 27:20.920
You...

27:22.240 --> 27:23.310
Lin Lu!

27:23.310 --> 27:24.550
Look at his attitude!

27:24.550 --> 27:26.720
How are we teachers supposed to teach him?

27:26.720 --> 27:28.580
-Director...
-What should we...

27:30.480 --> 27:31.960
Take them home

27:31.960 --> 27:33.820
and discipline them yourselves.

27:33.830 --> 27:36.490
Our teachers really can't
manage them anymore.

27:58.720 --> 28:00.350
Hello, Lin Lu. What's wrong?

28:00.350 --> 28:02.550
Ms. Lin, something happened to my boss!

28:03.160 --> 28:04.070
What happened to Qin Ao?

28:04.070 --> 28:05.550
His dad just called and said

28:05.550 --> 28:07.510
he hasn't gone home yet.

28:07.510 --> 28:08.880
Have you tried calling him?

28:08.880 --> 28:10.030
He got slapped at noon today.

28:10.030 --> 28:11.920
Then he just climbed over the wall
and left the school.

28:11.920 --> 28:13.750
He didn't even take his phone.

28:13.750 --> 28:15.200
What should we do now?

28:15.200 --> 28:15.960
How about

28:15.960 --> 28:16.920
I come to find you now,

28:16.920 --> 28:18.270
and we can go look for him together?

28:18.270 --> 28:19.110
No.

28:19.110 --> 28:20.240
It's too late now.

28:20.240 --> 28:20.960
Get some rest.

28:20.960 --> 28:22.090
I'll go look for him.

28:22.350 --> 28:23.920
-But he...
-No buts.

28:23.920 --> 28:24.790
Trust me.

28:30.350 --> 28:32.400
Hello. Qin Ao ran away from home.

28:32.640 --> 28:33.830
I'll wait for you downstairs.

28:33.830 --> 28:34.640
Let's go look for him together.

28:34.640 --> 28:35.350
Okay.

28:40.750 --> 28:41.550
Qin Ao!

28:43.110 --> 28:43.920
Qin Ao!

28:49.400 --> 28:50.240
Qin Ao!

28:56.680 --> 28:57.550
Did you find him?

28:57.550 --> 28:58.790
No. I'll check over there.

28:58.790 --> 28:59.310
Okay.

29:20.320 --> 29:21.780
Where else could Qin Ao be?

29:22.070 --> 29:23.530
We've looked everywhere.

29:28.310 --> 29:29.400
I just remembered.

29:29.920 --> 29:31.960
They have a secret hideout at school.

29:31.960 --> 29:32.790
Come with me.

29:42.270 --> 29:43.350
It's here.

29:46.310 --> 29:47.970
This is their secret hideout.

29:50.960 --> 29:51.790
Qin Ao.

29:54.510 --> 29:55.240
Qin Ao!

29:58.030 --> 29:58.880
Qin Ao!

30:00.920 --> 30:01.750
Qin Ao!

30:02.270 --> 30:03.310
Qin Ao!

30:05.400 --> 30:06.160
Qin Ao!

30:10.070 --> 30:10.960
Qin Ao!

30:17.270 --> 30:18.030
Qin Ao!

30:28.070 --> 30:29.110
Nothing.

30:30.310 --> 30:31.240
Not here either.

30:41.440 --> 30:43.030
Even without proof,

30:44.510 --> 30:45.740
I believe

30:46.590 --> 30:48.120
Qin Ao was wrongly accused.

30:51.440 --> 30:53.000
When you're a teenager,

30:54.160 --> 30:56.680
there's nothing worse
than being falsely accused—

30:56.680 --> 30:58.940
especially by the people closest to you.

31:06.270 --> 31:07.480
When I was little,

31:08.240 --> 31:09.500
my dad always said that

31:11.030 --> 31:12.590
when he got back from his business trip,

31:12.590 --> 31:14.000
he'd take me to the zoo.

31:15.070 --> 31:17.030
If I could place first in my year,

31:17.240 --> 31:18.640
he'd buy me balloons,

31:19.070 --> 31:20.030
toys,

31:20.790 --> 31:22.640
and everything I liked.

31:23.920 --> 31:25.790
But he never once kept his word.

31:30.070 --> 31:31.130
He said he was busy?

31:35.640 --> 31:36.640
So

31:37.200 --> 31:39.310
I saved up my allowance

31:39.960 --> 31:41.920
and bought all the things I liked.

31:43.640 --> 31:44.920
But when he saw them,

31:47.270 --> 31:49.870
he accused me of
stealing his money to buy them.

31:50.590 --> 31:52.050
He threw everything away.

31:57.310 --> 31:58.640
He didn't believe me.

32:03.110 --> 32:04.640
It's always been like this.

32:09.880 --> 32:11.340
What happened after that?

32:14.550 --> 32:15.880
Later, even when he

32:15.880 --> 32:17.440
found his money in the car,

32:18.350 --> 32:19.920
he didn't apologize to me.

32:26.680 --> 32:28.960
He might not even remember it now.

32:30.270 --> 32:31.470
But I still remember.

32:34.510 --> 32:36.570
The feeling of being wrongly accused

32:39.070 --> 32:40.870
is like a blade cutting into you.

32:42.750 --> 32:44.880
The pain stays with you for a long time.

32:57.330 --> 32:58.200
Wang Fa.

33:00.200 --> 33:01.790
We have to find Qin Ao

33:02.750 --> 33:03.790
and tell him

33:05.550 --> 33:07.510
that he deserves to be believed.

33:14.440 --> 33:15.270
Don't worry.

33:16.960 --> 33:18.030
We'll find him.

33:38.590 --> 33:40.550
Why did it suddenly start raining?

33:54.510 --> 33:55.510
Let's head back.

33:55.880 --> 33:57.640
Searching aimlessly at night

33:57.640 --> 33:58.770
isn't going to help.

33:59.030 --> 34:00.960
We'll keep looking in the morning.

34:01.030 --> 34:04.560
If we still can't find him after 24 hours,
we'll call the police.

34:05.830 --> 34:06.550
Okay.

34:06.790 --> 34:08.510
I'll call Qin Ao's father.

34:20.190 --> 34:21.389
Ms. Lin.

34:22.230 --> 34:23.710
Did you find him?

34:24.550 --> 34:25.280
What?

34:26.960 --> 34:29.670
Who knows where he ran off to?

34:30.550 --> 34:31.400
I'm sorry

34:31.760 --> 34:33.159
for causing you trouble.

34:34.110 --> 34:34.920
Okay.

34:35.710 --> 34:36.639
Don't worry.

34:36.840 --> 34:37.880
If I find him,

34:38.110 --> 34:39.840
I'll let you know immediately.

34:40.880 --> 34:41.400
Okay.

34:58.920 --> 34:59.890
Got it, Uncle.

35:01.000 --> 35:03.030
Qin Ao's dad said
he'd searched everywhere.

35:03.030 --> 35:03.960
Logically,

35:03.960 --> 35:05.760
he shouldn't have gone very far.

35:06.440 --> 35:07.840
I checked, and there are
a few internet cafes nearby.

35:07.840 --> 35:09.240
We can look around there.

35:09.880 --> 35:11.150
But you look terrible.

35:11.150 --> 35:12.610
Do you want to take a break?

35:13.030 --> 35:13.670
I'm fine.

35:16.880 --> 35:17.590
Lin Lu?

35:18.800 --> 35:20.030
Coach, Coach,

35:20.030 --> 35:21.510
my cousin's family works in construction.

35:21.510 --> 35:22.630
He just told me

35:22.630 --> 35:24.320
he thinks he saw Boss

35:24.320 --> 35:26.960
at the Hongjing New Village
construction site.

35:26.960 --> 35:28.490
Okay, we'll head there now.

35:29.190 --> 35:29.840
I've called a cab.

35:29.840 --> 35:30.670
Let's go.

35:31.630 --> 35:32.840
You see, he first says,

35:32.840 --> 35:34.400
"Leave it here, Xianglin's Wife."

35:34.400 --> 35:36.590
The tone here is much harsher.

35:36.590 --> 35:37.630
So his tone

35:37.630 --> 35:40.320
shows his dissatisfaction and disgust
towards her.

35:40.320 --> 35:42.320
But if he'd said,
"Xianglin's Wife, just leave it there,"

35:42.320 --> 35:43.960
wouldn't it sound a bit more polite?

35:43.960 --> 35:45.630
So by comparing the two ways of saying it,

35:45.630 --> 35:48.190
we can see the strong feelings expressed
by the author.

35:46.580 --> 35:47.630
[Okay, we'll head there now.]

35:48.190 --> 35:50.280
So, pay attention to this part.

35:53.760 --> 35:54.880
Not bad.

35:54.880 --> 35:56.680
Your accuracy rate is very high.

36:11.370 --> 36:12.800
[Found Qin Ao. Let's go.]

36:21.880 --> 36:23.940
-Lin Lu? Lin Lu.
-Lin Lu.

36:24.630 --> 36:25.320
Are you okay?

36:25.320 --> 36:26.150
What's wrong?

36:26.150 --> 36:27.470
-I'm dizzy... really dizzy...
-What happened?

36:27.470 --> 36:28.360
I feel very dizzy.

36:28.360 --> 36:28.840
What's wrong?

36:28.840 --> 36:30.590
He probably has low blood sugar again,

36:30.590 --> 36:31.630
ma'am.

36:31.630 --> 36:33.150
How about I take him
to the infirmary right now?

36:33.150 --> 36:34.320
-Okay, go quickly.
-Okay, okay.

36:34.320 --> 36:36.070
-Thank you, ma'am.
-I'm so dizzy...

36:36.070 --> 36:37.070
It's fine. Let's go.

36:37.070 --> 36:37.800
Be careful.

36:37.800 --> 36:38.760
Be careful. Careful.

36:38.760 --> 36:40.290
Thank you, ma'am. Goodbye.

36:41.440 --> 36:42.970
Everyone, self-study now.

36:43.440 --> 36:44.440
How did you know?

36:44.440 --> 36:45.400
From my phone.

36:45.560 --> 36:47.120
Didn't Jin Laoyao confiscate your phone?

36:46.010 --> 36:47.370
[Teachers' Office 3]

36:47.150 --> 36:48.280
Who told you I only had one?

36:47.390 --> 36:48.500
[Class 6, Grade 12]

36:48.280 --> 36:49.880
This is my mom's spare phone.

36:50.440 --> 36:51.590
Now, let's go over

36:51.590 --> 36:53.440
the strategies
for grammar cloze questions.

36:53.440 --> 36:55.440
First, these questions involve verbs,

36:55.440 --> 36:58.630
which can be divided into
finite and non-finite verbs.

36:58.630 --> 36:59.800
Finite verbs involve tense,

36:59.800 --> 37:01.710
and tense includes
past and perfect tenses.

37:01.710 --> 37:03.150
Everyone, turn your textbooks to

37:03.150 --> 37:04.280
-page 111.
-Chen Jianghe.

37:04.280 --> 37:07.540
-Do the second multiple-choice question.
-Chen Jianghe.

37:13.760 --> 37:14.320
Sir.

37:14.920 --> 37:15.720
What's wrong?

37:15.960 --> 37:17.030
My stomach hurts.

37:17.030 --> 37:18.560
I need to go to the restroom.

37:18.880 --> 37:19.510
Go.

37:20.350 --> 37:21.410
Come back quickly.

37:22.710 --> 37:24.280
The rest of you, continue.

37:25.280 --> 37:29.140
Everyone, pay attention to the changes
in the liquid in the test tube.

37:50.710 --> 37:51.880
In our last class,

37:51.880 --> 37:53.280
we talked about radicles and seedlings,

37:53.280 --> 37:54.550
but many of you couldn't distinguish

37:54.550 --> 37:56.280
which parts they refer to.

37:56.280 --> 37:57.030
Today, I'll explain them

37:57.030 --> 37:58.030
carefully again.

37:58.030 --> 37:59.490
First, we need to know that

37:59.510 --> 38:00.870
-radicles and seedlings
-Cover for me.

38:00.870 --> 38:02.590
contain small amounts of gibberellins

38:02.590 --> 38:04.510
and cytokinins.

38:04.510 --> 38:07.070
And they also have small amounts of
some other...

38:07.070 --> 38:08.830
-Ma'am! Ma'am!
-Ma'am!

38:08.850 --> 38:10.030
-He's not feeling well.
-He's not feeling well.

38:10.030 --> 38:10.670
He wants to go to the infirmary.

38:10.670 --> 38:11.510
What's wrong?

38:11.510 --> 38:13.230
-His stomach hurts.
-His head hurts.

38:13.230 --> 38:14.280
Where does it hurt?

38:14.280 --> 38:15.800
-His... His head hurts.
-His stomach hurts.

38:15.800 --> 38:17.190
Where exactly is he hurt?

38:17.190 --> 38:18.920
Ma'am, they both hurt a little.

38:19.190 --> 38:20.710
So much trouble. Go, go.

38:20.710 --> 38:21.360
-Go, go.
-Okay, okay.

38:21.360 --> 38:22.960
-Such a handful.
-Thank you, ma'am. Thank you.

38:22.960 --> 38:24.440
We'll be right back.

38:24.440 --> 38:25.440
I really can't hold on anymore.

38:25.440 --> 38:26.400
-Be right back, ma'am.
-Be right back, ma'am.

38:26.400 --> 38:27.800
Alright, the rest of you,
don't be distracted.

38:27.800 --> 38:28.960
Let's continue our class.

38:28.480 --> 38:32.550
[Class 1, Grade 12]

38:28.960 --> 38:30.280
Open your workbooks.

38:30.280 --> 38:31.880
Turn to Chapter 8, Section 8.

38:31.900 --> 38:32.900
Read carefully.

38:49.760 --> 38:50.760
Qin!

38:52.070 --> 38:53.600
Are you done with your work?

38:54.230 --> 38:55.030
Done!

38:55.790 --> 38:56.920
Come on, get down!

38:56.920 --> 38:58.980
Help unload the cement from the cart.

38:59.030 --> 39:00.000
Coming!

39:12.150 --> 39:13.980
[Beware of the Water]

39:20.440 --> 39:21.190
Be careful.

39:29.070 --> 39:30.170
[Caution: Fall Hazard]

39:29.560 --> 39:30.330
Qin Ao!

39:35.730 --> 39:36.600
Wait.

39:36.200 --> 39:38.710
[Caution: Fall Hazard]

39:42.480 --> 39:44.230
Coach, Ms. Lin,

39:44.470 --> 39:45.550
why are you here?

39:45.570 --> 39:47.170
We should be asking you that.

39:47.800 --> 39:48.760
Why are you here?

39:52.330 --> 39:53.210
Just leave.

39:54.110 --> 39:55.440
Stop worrying about me.

39:56.360 --> 39:57.360
My dad is right.

39:57.780 --> 40:00.310
I was born to
carry cement and tighten screws.

40:03.670 --> 40:04.190
Just go.

40:05.280 --> 40:06.320
Boss!

40:06.320 --> 40:07.000
Qin Ao!

40:07.020 --> 40:07.770
-Qin Ao!
-Qin Ao.

40:07.770 --> 40:09.150
-Ao!
-Ao!

40:10.400 --> 40:11.530
-Qin Ao!
-Come here.

40:11.840 --> 40:13.440
Where have you been?

40:15.840 --> 40:17.770
We've been worried sick about you.

40:28.630 --> 40:29.830
Don't worry about me.

40:30.960 --> 40:32.690
I mean it. Don't worry about me.

40:33.230 --> 40:34.960
Hit me, yell at me—I don't care.

40:35.190 --> 40:35.840
Just go.

40:36.190 --> 40:37.230
I think you're
really asking for a beating.

40:37.230 --> 40:38.590
What are you talking about?

40:38.590 --> 40:40.550
Since when did you become such a coward?

40:40.550 --> 40:41.590
We're all here.

40:43.700 --> 40:45.630
We'll go with you to see Jin Laoyao.

40:47.070 --> 40:47.920
Ms. Lin.

40:49.710 --> 40:50.710
Take them and go.

40:51.480 --> 40:52.400
This is a construction site.

40:52.400 --> 40:53.920
It's crowded

40:54.230 --> 40:55.230
and really messy.

40:56.480 --> 40:57.300
Qin Ao!

40:57.320 --> 40:59.210
Aren't we a team?

40:59.760 --> 41:01.480
Yeah. Worst case,
we all haul bricks together!

41:01.480 --> 41:03.080
Right. I'll go get hard hats.

41:03.670 --> 41:05.070
I'll work with you, Boss.

41:05.920 --> 41:06.840
Come on, come on.

41:06.840 --> 41:07.550
I'll help you, Boss.

41:07.550 --> 41:09.000
Look at you, like a drowned rat.

41:09.000 --> 41:10.800
Just looking at you ticks me off.

41:11.110 --> 41:12.110
Give me a hand.

41:15.550 --> 41:16.610
What are you doing?

41:16.920 --> 41:18.250
Let go! Let go!

41:18.270 --> 41:19.480
Sorry! Sorry!

41:19.480 --> 41:21.550
They're students
from Hongjing No. 8 High School.

41:21.550 --> 41:22.920
I'm their teacher.

41:22.920 --> 41:24.960
We're here for a work-study program.

41:24.960 --> 41:26.140
We're doing it for free.

41:26.140 --> 41:28.800
We just need you
to write us a certificate later.

41:30.710 --> 41:31.150
Don't mention it.

41:31.150 --> 41:33.110
Ms. Lin reacted so fast.

41:33.110 --> 41:34.760
-Hurry.
-Come on.

41:53.030 --> 41:54.400
Come on, come on.

41:57.630 --> 41:59.000
Be careful, everyone.

41:59.000 --> 42:00.360
What a bunch of idiots.

42:01.110 --> 42:02.030
Take it easy.

42:02.550 --> 42:03.550
Yeah,

42:03.550 --> 42:04.710
a bunch of idiots.

42:05.710 --> 42:06.840
They insist on calling you "Boss"

42:06.840 --> 42:08.440
and helping you haul bricks.

42:10.360 --> 42:12.820
Do you really
have the heart to abandon them?

42:15.880 --> 42:17.880
It's not that I want to abandon them.

42:20.550 --> 42:22.350
It's that I don't want to go back.

42:26.230 --> 42:28.360
My dad's always looked down on me.

42:30.760 --> 42:32.470
I wasn't lying. I...

42:33.840 --> 42:34.510
I really wasn't lying.

42:34.510 --> 42:36.110
Why won't anyone believe me?

42:36.190 --> 42:37.190
We believe you.

42:38.800 --> 42:39.590
Me,

42:40.280 --> 42:41.150
Coach Wang,

42:43.440 --> 42:45.110
and your buddies here—

42:46.590 --> 42:48.000
we all believe you.

42:56.800 --> 42:59.190
Qin Ao, don't run away from this.

42:59.670 --> 43:01.110
You should prove to those

43:01.110 --> 43:03.150
who don't believe you

43:03.210 --> 43:04.420
that they're wrong.

43:03.630 --> 43:04.680
♪ The night sky and starlight ♪

43:05.520 --> 43:09.970
♪ Secret words falling into my palm ♪

43:08.670 --> 43:10.000
Will they ever admit it?

43:10.810 --> 43:12.090
♪ Unraveling the mystery ♪

43:10.920 --> 43:11.630
They will.

43:12.850 --> 43:16.880
♪ It was you who gave me this brilliance ♪

43:17.910 --> 43:19.090
♪ Lasting memories ♪

43:20.020 --> 43:24.520
♪ The distance
that brings our dreams closer ♪

43:25.120 --> 43:25.980
♪ To run toward you ♪

43:26.670 --> 43:31.250
♪ I keep practicing with no turning back ♪

43:34.720 --> 43:36.000
♪ There's nothing to fear ♪

43:37.190 --> 43:38.520
♪ Because you're with me ♪

43:41.670 --> 43:42.920
♪ The light shimmers ♪
